00:44:13,970 --> 00:44:16,200
Ah, sure! Please give us some fried mandoo, too.

504
00:44:16,200 --> 00:44:17,970
Sure.

505
00:45:16,090 --> 00:45:18,060
Oh, Joon Jae!

