508
00:45:32,880 --> 00:45:35,310
- Bye.- Bye.

509
00:45:51,700 --> 00:45:54,800
Heo Joon Jae, are you mad at me now?

510
00:46:04,540 --> 00:46:08,310
You guys fought again? Why do you fight every day?

511
00:46:08,310 --> 00:46:13,090
I met Heo Joon Jae's older brother today, and
