continuing the relationship with her.

514
00:46:19,960 --> 00:46:23,430
What? You met his older brother? How?

515
00:46:23,430 --> 00:46:25,600
He came to have a meal with me.

516
00:46:25,600 --> 00:46:28,570
I thought he wasn't keeping in touch
with any of his family members.

517
00:46:28,570 --> 00:46:30,970
I've never been introduced to them, either.

518
00:46:30,970 --> 00:46:32,170
You've been introduced?

519
00:46:32,170 --> 00:46:35,070
Yes. The last, last, last time.

520
00:47:02,300 --> 00:47:04,440
What's wrong?

521
00:47:06,570 --> 00:47:09,340
Is it because it's been so long
