than me, they won't be able to get into our house.

525
00:47:31,900 --> 00:47:35,970
Okay. That fine. Also, go out and stay out today.

526
00:47:35,970 --> 00:47:38,700
Why? I don't have any plans.

527
00:47:40,210 --> 00:47:43,440
Hyung, you get out, too.
Don't come back until the evening.

528
00:47:43,440 --> 00:47:45,540
What should I do that?

529
00:47:45,540 --> 00:47:48,610
This is my house. When the house
owner tells you to do so, you do it.

530
00:47:48,610 --> 00:47:54,290
Wow, he is making us pitiful again. Where
could we go in this harsh winter weather?

531
00:47:54,290 --> 00:47:59,560
Since you said you are not going to work,
it's so hard to even set up a meeting.

532
00:48:00,960 --> 00:48:03,330
Okay. Well, then, today,

533
00:48:03,330 --> 00:48:07,830
no one will come back home
until the evening, right?

534
00:48:09,100 --> 00:48:11,700
Get out. Hurry! Out!

535
00:48:11,700 --> 00:48:15,370
- I need to get changed! - Just come out.
- I'm going to get changed first.

536
00:48:15,370 --> 00:48:17,610
Hurry and come out. I'll wait out there.

537
00:48:39,530 --> 00:48:44,140
Until the evening, no one will come?

538
00:48:52,210 --> 00:48:56,950
Aish, it's so cold and where is he telling me to go?

539
00:49:47,270 --> 00:49:50,000
I was wondering what you were doing.

540
00:49:50,000 --> 00:49:55,240
Are you not cold?
Why are you swimming during the winter?

541
00:50:16,160 --> 00:50:21,800
What... What are you wearing? What's on your body?

542
00:50:24,170 --> 00:50:29,940
Ah, you're going to do a part-time job
