543
00:50:29,940 --> 00:50:32,380
Our Cheong is so funny!

544
00:50:32,380 --> 00:50:38,780
For a moment, I thought you were
a merm— Hah! What am I saying?

545
00:50:38,780 --> 00:50:43,260
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I've been
watching too much American drama.

546
00:50:43,260 --> 00:50:47,390
It really looks like the real thing.
I'm thinking about something impossible...

547
00:50:48,960 --> 00:50:52,030
Miss, where's your house?

548
00:50:52,030 --> 00:50:54,100
My house is far away.

549
00:50:54,100 --> 00:50:55,430
There are a lot of things like this at my house.

550
00:50:55,430 --> 00:50:57,970
That female patient.
