551
00:50:57,970 --> 00:51:00,310
Is it true that she regained her consciousness
with just one round of the defibrillator?

552
00:51:00,310 --> 00:51:01,510
In just one week,

553
00:51:01,510 --> 00:51:05,380
- this turned into this? - Does that make any sense?

554
00:51:05,380 --> 00:51:06,750
Where'd you get this?

555
00:51:06,750 --> 00:51:09,610
I worked hard to make this.

556
00:51:19,390 --> 00:51:21,330
No way...

557
00:51:29,770 --> 00:51:32,570
Can you give me the gown over there?

558
00:51:42,850 --> 00:51:45,580
What is this? This— What?

559
00:51:48,550 --> 00:51:52,660
This. What is this? Huh?

560
00:51:52,660 --> 00:51:55,830
How... How did it change?

561
00:51:58,800 --> 00:52:01,530
Wow, there really are things
like this in the world!

562
00:52:01,530 --> 00:52:02,880
Wow! What the!

563
00:52:02,880 --> 00:52:04,440
Do I need to report you to
some international topic news,

564
00:52:04,440 --> 00:52:07,010
I mean FBI or something?

565
00:52:07,010 --> 00:52:08,540
Are you going to tell Heo Joon Jae?

566
00:52:08,540 --> 00:52:13,410
Tell him? Uh, I'm not sure.

567
00:52:13,410 --> 00:52:16,420
After I see how you reply to my questions.

568
00:52:18,050 --> 00:52:20,390
Don't come close.

569
00:52:21,190 --> 00:52:25,190
So, when you go into the water,
you turn into what you were before,

570
00:52:25,190 --> 00:52:28,060
and if you come out of the water, you grow legs?

571
00:52:28,060 --> 00:52:29,430
Yeah.

572
00:52:29,430 --> 00:52:31,430
Wow! I'm going crazy!

573
00:52:32,100 --> 00:52:37,970
So, the pearl? The pearl from last time. Like how it
is in the fairy tales, it was made from your tears?

574
00:52:37,970 --> 00:52:39,600
That's right.

575
00:52:40,670 --> 00:52:42,340
Cry.

576
00:52:45,080 --> 00:52:51,050
Cry. Let me see if it really turns into pearls.
It's because I'm fascinated right now.

577
00:52:56,460 --> 00:53:00,690
Okay, well, you don't have to cry right
now. Let's slowly cry a lot from now on.

578
00:53:01,690 --> 00:53:03,860
Wow! This is a jackpot!

579
00:53:03,860 --> 00:53:07,000
Since I replied well, you're not
going to tell Heo Joon Jae, right?

580
00:53:07,000 --> 00:53:12,600
Cheong! Mermaid Cheong!
Why should we keep this a secret?

581
00:53:12,600 --> 00:53:16,170
This is an amazing thing!
We are sitting on a pile of money!

582
00:53:16,170 --> 00:53:17,740
I don't like a pile of money!

583
00:53:17,740 --> 00:53:21,150
I like it! What's the point of staying home?

584
00:53:21,150 --> 00:53:25,020
Hey! Let's go to a place like Las Vegas together,

585
00:53:25,020 --> 00:53:29,860
launch a mermaid show, and go on a world tour!

586
00:53:29,860 --> 00:53:31,990
Are you saying you're going
to sell me off, Jo Nam Doo?

587
00:53:31,990 --> 00:53:37,230
No! I'm recommending a job to you. It's hard
for a normal person to get a job these days.

588
00:53:37,230 --> 00:53:40,870
Since it's me, I am not reporting
you to any national agencies,

589
00:53:40,870 --> 00:53:43,740
and am going to look into
going overseas for work.

590
00:53:44,740 --> 00:53:47,310
- Okay! - Okay?

591
00:53:47,310 --> 00:53:48,740
Yeah.

592
00:53:49,740 --> 00:53:51,340
Okay.

593
00:53:52,240 --> 00:53:55,510
- You want to shake hands?- Yeah, let's shake hands.

594
00:53:59,120 --> 00:54:02,050
It's not something contagious, right?

595
00:54:03,760 --> 00:54:05,320
Okay, fine.

596
00:54:28,380 --> 00:54:30,550
Jo Nam Doo, are you okay?

597
00:54:33,390 --> 00:54:36,590
Were you swimming here?

598
00:54:36,590 --> 00:54:39,320
Is it not cold in this winter?

599
00:54:48,330 --> 00:54:52,970
If Heo Joon Jae also sees my real
self, would he act like Jo Nam Doo?

600
00:54:52,970 --> 00:54:57,110
Since I was already caught, should I have
asked him first before erasing his memories?

601
00:54:57,110 --> 00:54:58,410
Jo Nam Doo!

602
00:54:58,410 --> 00:55:02,150
Are you not cold?
Why are you swimming during the winter?

603
00:55:06,590 --> 00:55:07,650
What are you wearing?

604
00:55:07,650 --> 00:55:09,860
Wanting to get a part-time... I... you... a mermaid!

605
00:55:09,860 --> 00:55:11,220
Can I touch it?

606
00:55:11,220 --> 00:55:11,990
Wow, I'm going crazy!

607
00:55:11,990 --> 00:55:13,230
This is amazing!

608
00:55:13,230 --> 00:55:17,430
Try crying. We are now sitting on a pile of money!

609
00:55:18,400 --> 00:55:23,240
You know all of the truth, so you probably
can't see me the same way as before, right?

610
00:55:23,240 --> 00:55:26,640
Of course not! To be honest, it's hard
to see you in the same way as before.

611
00:55:26,640 --> 00:55:28,110
Would Heo Joon Jae also be like this?

612
00:55:28,110 --> 00:55:33,550
He will be worse than me! If he sees
something like this, he will run away 100%!

613
00:55:33,550 --> 00:55:35,680
Then I probably should never be caught.

614
00:55:35,680 --> 00:55:38,980
But it's too late because I found out.

615
00:55:42,090 --> 00:55:44,160
To be honest, I was questioning
whether or not it would work

616
00:55:44,160 --> 00:55:45,990
since I've only done it once in the water.

617
00:55:45,990 --> 00:55:48,230
But it works well outside of the water too.

618
00:55:48,230 --> 00:55:49,830
What?

619
00:55:54,300 --> 00:55:57,100
I'm sorry.

620
00:56:15,120 --> 00:56:17,320
I'm going crazy.

621
00:56:18,420 --> 00:56:23,800
You know that feeling. When you're about to
think of something, but it doesn't come out.

622
00:56:23,800 --> 00:56:27,100
What should I do? Does he remember?

623
00:56:27,100 --> 00:56:32,240
Something like seeing the lottery number
in your dreams and then not remembering it.

624
00:56:32,240 --> 00:56:35,370
That frustration that makes you go crazy!

625
00:56:35,370 --> 00:56:38,440
I erased it, but did it not erase well?

626
00:56:38,440 --> 00:56:42,810
Wait! I think I remember something.

627
00:56:45,850 --> 00:56:50,620
That... In this house's swimming pool...

628
00:56:52,260 --> 00:56:54,260
Cheong...!

629
00:56:57,960 --> 00:56:59,430
Ow, why did you hit me?

630
00:56:59,430 --> 00:57:01,600
Eat instead of being loud.

631
00:57:01,600 --> 00:57:05,940
Hey, look! Look at my toes.

632
00:57:05,940 --> 00:57:09,410
I feel like my toenail is going
to fall off! But I don't remember!

633
00:57:09,410 --> 00:57:14,310
How my foot became like this,
how my foot bumped into something!

634
00:57:14,310 --> 00:57:16,980
I just can't remember anything!

635
00:57:16,980 --> 00:57:19,580
- It's early dementia due to alcohol.  - Is that it?

636
00:57:19,580 --> 00:57:22,090
So watch your drinking!

637
00:57:22,090 --> 00:57:24,020
Ah, put it down.

638
00:57:25,460 --> 00:57:28,960
I didn't want to live smearing poop on the wall.

639
00:57:28,960 --> 00:57:30,900
How can I be like this already?

640
00:57:30,900 --> 00:57:34,500
There are supposed to be three bad luck
events this year. Has it started already?

641
00:57:51,780 --> 00:57:53,550
Until when are you going to be like this?

642
00:57:53,550 --> 00:57:54,320
What?

643
00:57:54,320 --> 00:57:58,760
You're not talking to me or
meeting my eyes or smiling.

644
00:57:59,490 --> 00:58:04,130
Okay, then. Let me ask one more time.
If something happens to me...

645
00:58:04,130 --> 00:58:06,300
It's the same even if you ask a hundred times.

646
00:58:06,300 --> 00:58:10,170
If something happens to you, I can't live.

647
00:58:10,170 --> 00:58:11,840
Yeah, so why?

648
00:58:11,840 --> 00:58:13,540
That...

649
00:58:14,840 --> 00:58:19,750
My heart can only beat if you love me.

650
00:58:23,580 --> 00:58:28,420
My heart on land has a limited time.

651
00:58:28,420 --> 00:58:35,360
If you leave me or leave this
world, my heartbeat stops.

652
00:58:36,090 --> 00:58:38,800
Jung Hoon died because of that, too.

653
00:58:38,800 --> 00:58:42,700
When a loved one leaves, the heart cools,

654
00:58:42,700 --> 00:58:45,600
hardens, and stops.

655
00:58:46,440 --> 00:58:49,410
Without you, I'll be like that.

656
00:58:50,180 --> 00:58:54,410
Unless I return to the ocean, I'll probably die.

657
00:58:55,280 --> 00:58:57,280
You're going to die?

658
00:59:02,390 --> 00:59:04,490
What?

659
00:59:04,490 --> 00:59:07,390
- What did you just say?  - What?

660
00:59:07,430 --> 00:59:13,630
Say it again. What will stop, harden?
What will happen?

661
00:59:14,600 --> 00:59:16,370
You hear my voice?

662
00:59:16,370 --> 00:59:18,540
You said your heart will stop.

663
00:59:18,540 --> 00:59:20,010
When did you start hearing it?

664
00:59:20,110 --> 00:59:22,370
- You said you're going to die.
- When did you start hearing it?

665
00:59:22,410 --> 00:59:24,180
Why are you going to die?!

666
00:59:24,180 --> 00:59:28,850
♬ Seeing with you; Listening with you;♬

667
00:59:28,850 --> 00:59:33,190
♬Breathing with you. Everything.♬

668
00:59:33,190 --> 00:59:37,660
♬There's nothing to throw away. I'm so happy.♬

669
00:59:37,660 --> 00:59:41,930
♬ I want to stop by your side. ♬

670
00:59:41,930 --> 00:59:45,800
♬ Everything about you ♬

671
00:59:45,800 --> 00:59:50,870
♬I cannot remember ♬

672
00:59:50,870 --> 00:59:54,140
♬I am ♬

673
00:59:54,140 --> 00:59:55,640
There is something I need to ask you.

674
00:59:55,640 --> 00:59:56,910
Is that important to you now?

675
00:59:56,910 --> 00:59:58,210
Did you look for Kang Ji Yeon?

676
00:59:58,210 --> 01:00:00,710
I've never done a background
check that gave me such a chill.

677
01:00:00,710 --> 01:00:03,620
You said you are going to quit your job.
How about my house?

678
01:00:03,620 --> 01:00:06,150
You've gotten much better.

679
01:00:06,150 --> 01:00:08,620
I'm going to do a birthday party at home.
Can you come?

680
01:00:08,620 --> 01:00:09,250
I'll be there.

681
01:00:09,250 --> 01:00:10,560
I have a good idea.

682
01:00:10,560 --> 01:00:12,020
What are you talking about?

683
01:00:12,020 --> 01:00:15,060
Let's do like this. Trust me and leave it up to me.
